headline: Jacobs Selected to Support Idaho Airport Expansion
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was chosen by the Boise Airport to support its multi-year capital expansion plan, including the construction of Concourse A, the renovation of Concourse B and potential improvements to other terminal facilities to accommodate an 81% increase in passenger demand during the past decade.
